{"id": "art-172", "label": "Art. 172", "title": "Art. 172: Actele încheiate de cel care beneficiază de consiliere judiciară sau tutelă specială", "slug": "art-172", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2057282236\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1221\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2057282236\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 172: Actele\nîncheiate de cel care beneficiaz&#259; de consiliere judiciar&#259; sau\ntutel&#259; special&#259; </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1361844603\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1220\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1361844603\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Actele juridice încheiate de persoana care\nbeneficiaz&#259; de m&#259;sura consilierii judiciare sau a tutelei speciale,\naltele decât cele prev&#259;zute la art. 41 alin. (3) &#351;i la art. 43 alin.\n(3), precum &#351;i cele autorizate de instan&#355;a de tutel&#259;, sunt\nanulabile sau presta&#355;iile care decurg din acestea pot fi reduse, chiar\nf&#259;r&#259; dovedirea unui prejudiciu &#351;i chiar dac&#259; la data\nîncheierii lor aceasta ar fi avut discern&#259;mânt.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1425629338\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1219\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1425629338\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Actele juridice încheiate înaintea instituirii\nconsilierii judiciare sau tutelei speciale pot fi anulate sau presta&#355;iile\ncare decurg din acestea pot fi reduse numai dac&#259; la data când au fost\nîncheiate lipsa discern&#259;mântului era notorie sau cunoscut&#259; de\ncealalt&#259; parte.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1105618499\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1218\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1105618499\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Dispozi&#355;iile testamentare f&#259;cute de persoana\nocrotit&#259; dup&#259; instituirea consilierii judiciare sunt valabile,\ndac&#259; sunt autorizate sau confirmate de c&#259;tre instan&#355;a de\ntutel&#259;, &#355;inând seama de natura acestora &#351;i circumstan&#355;ele\nîn care au fost f&#259;cute.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}